  "description": "Xero is cloud-native accounting software founded in New Zealand in 2006 [citation needed]. It\u0026rsquo;s widely used in Australia, New Zealand, and the UK, and has expanded into the US market.\n¶What It Does Xero provides invoicing, bill management, bank reconciliation, expense claims, purchase orders, and multi-currency accounting. It connects to banks for automatic transaction feeds, supports receipt capture, and integrates with a large marketplace of third-party apps for payroll, inventory, point-of-sale, and other functions.\n",
